      "url": "https://www.evidentlyai.com/llm-guide/llm-benchmarks",
      "description": "LLM benchmarks are standardized tests for LLM evaluations. This guide covers 30 benchmarks from MMLU to Chatbot Arena, with links to datasets and ...",
