      "title": "LLM Evaluation: Benchmarks vs. Human Judgment - Medium",
      "url": "https://medium.com/@lmpo/llm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0",
      "description": "Core Concept: A powerful “judge” LLM is tasked with scoring the quality of a target LLM's response based on a predefined grading rubric and a reference answer.",
