            "markdown": "[Sitemap](https://medium.com/sitemap/sitemap.xml)\n\n[Open in app](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.medium.reader&referrer=utm_source%3DmobileNavBar&source=post_page---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------------------------)\n\nSign up\n\n[Sign in](https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=login&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0&source=post_page---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------global_nav------------------)\n\n[Medium Logo](https://medium.com/?source=post_page---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------------------------)\n\nGet app\n\n[Write](https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fnew-story&source=---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------new_post_topnav------------------)\n\n[Search](https://medium.com/search?source=post_page---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------------------------)\n\nSign up\n\n[Sign in](https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=login&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0&source=post_page---top_nav_layout_nav-----------------------global_nav------------------)\n\n![](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*dmbNkD5D-u45r44go_cf0g.png)\n\nMember-only story\n\n# LLM Evaluation: Benchmarks vs. Human Judgment\n\n[![LM Po](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*8biNIOdTZO6v4MDdtPmm2Q.png)](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---byline--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[LM Po](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---byline--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\nFollow\n\n10 min read\n\n·\n\nOct 29, 2025\n\n1\n\n[Listen](https://medium.com/m/signin?actionUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fplans%3Fdimension%3Dpost_audio_button%26postId%3Df1cdd16098c0&operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0&source=---header_actions--f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_audio_button------------------)\n\nShare\n\nHow do we know which AI model is “best”? It’s a simple question that often leads to a complex answer. We see leaderboards, benchmarks, and scores that seem to offer a clear ranking, but the reality of how these models are evaluated is far more nuanced. The most common methods for grading Large Language Models (LLMs) have surprising limitations that aren’t immediately obvious from a quick glance at a chart. This article peels back the curtain on LLM evaluation. To understand these truths, it helps to know that evaluation methods generally fall into two camps: objective, **benchmark-based** tests and subjective, **judgment-based** rankings. We will explain the fundamental difference between these two “families” of evaluation, providing a clear and detailed map for any learner new to the topic.\n\n**If you’re not a Medium subscriber,** [**click here to read the full article**](https://medium.com/@lmpo/llm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0?sk=ea61653d5616dbfff28f98337904f87d) **.**\n\nPress enter or click to view image in full size\n\n![](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:700/0*I2BmGlEaiUPkjxvc.png)\n\n[Benchmark performance of DeepSeek-V3 and its counterparts](https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.19437).\n\n## 1\\. Overview of the Four Core Evaluation Approaches\n\nThe evaluation of trained LLMs is a multifaceted challenge. The prevailing methods can be classified into four distinct approaches, which are further grouped into two main types: **benchmark-based evaluation** and **judgment-based evaluation**. While metrics such as training loss, perplexity, and rewards are used internally during model development, the following four methods are common in…\n\n**1\\. Benchmark-Based Evaluation:** These methods rely on standardized datasets and objective, quantifiable metrics.\n\n- **Evaluating Answer-Choice Accuracy (Multiple-Choice)**\n- **Using Verifiers to Check Answers**\n\n**2\\. Judgment-Based Evaluation:** These methods rely on subjective assessments, often of qualitative aspects like style or helpfulness.\n\n- **Leaderboards and Preference Ranking**\n- **LLM-as-a-Judge**\n\n## 2\\. Benchmark-Based Evaluation: Measuring Against a “Correct” Answer\n\nBenchmark-based evaluation provides a quantitative way to assess an LLM’s **factual recall** or **task-solving ability**. It’s akin to giving the model a standardized exam — with a set of right and wrong answers.\n\n## Create an account to read the full story.\n\nThe author made this story available to Medium members only.\n\nIf you’re new to Medium, create a new account to read this story on us.\n\n[Continue in app](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.medium.reader&referrer=utm_source%3Dregwall&source=-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------)\n\nOr, continue in mobile web\n\n[Sign up with Google](https://medium.com/m/connect/google?state=google-%7Chttps%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0%3Fsource%3D-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------%26skipOnboarding%3D1%7Cregister%7Cremember_me&source=-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------)\n\n[Sign up with Facebook](https://medium.com/m/connect/facebook?state=facebook-%7Chttps%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0%3Fsource%3D-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------%26skipOnboarding%3D1%7Cregister%7Cremember_me&source=-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------)\n\nSign up with email\n\nAlready have an account? [Sign in](https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=login&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0&source=-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------post_regwall------------------)\n\n[![LM Po](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:48:48/1*8biNIOdTZO6v4MDdtPmm2Q.png)](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---post_author_info--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[![LM Po](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:64:64/1*8biNIOdTZO6v4MDdtPmm2Q.png)](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---post_author_info--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\nFollow\n\n[**Written by LM Po**](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---post_author_info--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[1K followers](https://medium.com/@lmpo/followers?source=post_page---post_author_info--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n· [65 following](https://medium.com/@lmpo/following?source=post_page---post_author_info--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\nFollow\n\n## No responses yet\n\n![](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*dmbNkD5D-u45r44go_cf0g.png)\n\nWrite a response\n\n[What are your thoughts?](https://medium.com/m/signin?operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40lmpo%2Fllm-evaluation-benchmarks-vs-human-judgment-f1cdd16098c0&source=---post_responses--f1cdd16098c0---------------------respond_sidebar------------------)\n\nCancel\n\nRespond\n\n## More from LM Po\n\n[See all from LM Po](https://medium.com/@lmpo?source=post_page---author_recirc--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n## Recommended from Medium\n\n[See more recommendations](https://medium.com/?source=post_page---read_next_recirc--f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[Help](https://help.medium.com/hc/en-us?source=post_page-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[Status](https://status.medium.com/?source=post_page-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[About](https://medium.com/about?autoplay=1&source=post_page-----f1cdd16098c0---------------------------------------)\n\n[Careers](https://medium.com/jobs-at-medium/work-at-medium-959d1a85284